There’s something about this place that just hits different.
@royalchinadelhi at @the.chanakya isn’t just a restaurant — it’s an experience. The vibe, the flavors, the presentation… everything feels thoughtfully done. From crispy dim sums to rich Cantonese mains, every bite was comfort with a twist.

If you’re into good food with even better ambiance — you need to check this one out.
